    "description": {
      "value": "<p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: justify\">You shout fiery prayers of pain and torment, with a burning hatred in your voice. If wielding a whip, it counts as Magical and any target struck receives an @Condition[Ablaze] Condition. For every subsequent Round in which they are entangled by the whip, they receive a further @Condition[Ablaze] Condition. Any living target struck must pass a <strong>Challenging (+0) Cool </strong>Test or scream in agony. If they fail the test, they lose their next Move; if failed by -3 or more SL, the target gains a @Condition[Stunned] Condition; if failed by -6 or more SL, the target gains the @Condition[Unconscious] Condition and is permanently scarred, waking up 1d10 Rounds later. Further, struck targets lose any @Condition[Bleeding] Conditions as their wounds cauterize; similarly, attacks from your whip cannot cause any @Condition[Bleeding] Conditions.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">Â </span></p>"
